msgid ""
"# Robe of the Archmagi _Wondrous item, legendary (requires attunement by a "
"sorcerer, warlock, or wizard)_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/robe_of_the_archmagi.md:8
msgid ""
"This elegant garment is made from exquisite cloth of white, gray, or black "
"and adorned with silvery runes. The robe's color corresponds to the "
"alignment for which the item was created. A white robe was made for good, "
"gray for neutral, and black for evil. You can't attune to a **robe of the "
"archmagi** that doesn't correspond to your alignment. You gain these "
"benefits while wearing the robe:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/robe_of_the_archmagi.md:11
msgid ""
"If you aren't wearing armor, your base Armor Class is 15 + your Dexterity "
"modifier."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/robe_of_the_archmagi.md:11
msgid ""
"You have advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical "
"effects."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/robe_of_the_archmagi.md:11
msgid "Your spell save DC and spell attack bonus each increase by 2."
msgstr ""
